r content.</p>\n<p>It ships with custom widgets, shortcodes, color schemes, social media integration, and a custom logo area. The theme options panel and live theme customizer can be used to easily manage theme settings.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-lenscap/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lenscap\" rel=\"nofollow\">29. Lenscap</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-lenscap/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lenscap\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/lenscap.jpg\" alt=\"Lenscap\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221685\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/lenscap.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/lenscap-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/lenscap-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Lenscap is a WordPress WooCommerce theme to sell online magazines, books, and literary material. It has built-in sections to add your content beautifully on the homepage of your website.</p>\n<p>It has elegant product page templates, image galleries, a custom header, a product search area, product categories, and filters. It&#8217;s a highly customizable theme with flexible options for your online store.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojo-marketplace-highend/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Highend\" rel=\"nofollow\">30. Highend</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojo-marketplace-highend/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Highend\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/highend.jpg\" alt=\"Highend Theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"398\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-219365\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/highend.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/highend-300x154.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/highend-768x394.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Highend is a modern WordPress theme for your WooCommerce store. It comes with multiple page layouts, a drag and drop page builder, multiple sidebars, and more.</p>\n<p>It supports custom fonts, social integrations, color skins, widget areas, and featured product sections. Highend is a beginner-friendly theme with multilingual support out of the box.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/artisanthemes-indigo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Indigo\" rel=\"nofollow\">31. Indigo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/artisanthemes-indigo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Indigo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/indigo.jpg\" alt=\"Indigo\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222211\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/indigo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/indigo-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/indigo-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Indigo is a WordPress theme with full WooCommerce support and designed to create an online store you need. It ships with a page builder that can be used to design your custom page layouts easily.</p>\n<p>You can also use their built-in page templates to quickly launch your online shop. It includes custom widgets, social sharing icons, pricing tables, contact form support, and multiple page layouts.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce-toyshop/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"ToyShop\" rel=\"nofollow\">32. Toyshop</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce-toyshop/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"ToyShop\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/toyshop.jpg\" alt=\"ToyShop\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222212\" srcset=\"https://www.isitw