(1577, 233, 'team_2_about', 'Minh Ho is Creative-Lab\'s Technical Leader. Minh Ho has nearly 8 years of experience in software development, he has worked on numerous platforms including Web, Mobile, Core Service, expert on many computer languages such as CSS3, HTML, Javascript, PHP, Angular JS, Node JS, React JS, Python, MySQL, PostgreSQL... and has worked in a broad range of software development positions such as developer, database designer and team leader. Minh\'s work experience includes analysis and design of web architecture, development and management.\r\n\r\nMinh Ho has a Bachelor\'s Degree in Network, Programming from University of Science in Vietnam.'),
